{"tid":275313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[只准買支那垃圾債救支爆]  木馬李小加：債券通南向2年內不會開通","createTime":"2017-06-08T02:42:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T08:02:54.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"44344e40f8d1ca49b3e6298a6f8aea8a6107cdd2","tid":275313,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T02:42:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>不平等條約</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=al3u4Y9mZyU%2BqV7qNFCnK54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=8089819e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】香港交易所(00388)行政總裁李小加稱，「債券通」南向於2年內不會開通。<br />\n<br />\n「債券通」已確認初期先開通「北向」交易，不設額度限制，暫時亦只容許機構投資者參與。「債券通」的意義在於利用港交所的交易平台及金管局的結算系統，讓境外投資者買內地債券，推動內地債市的開放和國際化。<br />\n<br />\n對於有報道稱，債券通會在七一前後實施，人民銀行與金管局的聯合公告表示，在完成相關規則和系統建設、回應市場參與者實際需求及獲得相關監管許可後，便會正式啟動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170608/20170608094521fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170608%2F20170608094521fi.html&d=al3u4Y9mZyU%2BqV7qNFCnK54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f55c38d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170608/20170608094521fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"58cc5fdc338357b1bada2cc42dcaffe8a7d19200","tid":275313,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T03:48:07.000Z","msg":"根本所有乜乜通都係泵水去鄰國啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fd15c8e4379e34fc67e1814b5f9331751729e6","tid":275313,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T03:50:44.000Z","msg":"有入冇出"},{"pid":"bec782ff38c8a496e5b1b39dd79a880167a16a00","tid":275313,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:00:27.000Z","msg":"點樣防止被買呢啲垃圾債券"},{"pid":"198424705947c2f2d1412f9fd0ae1aae33559330","tid":275313,"uid":68099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:20:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣防止被買呢啲垃圾債券</blockquote><br />\n好難，對於班fund佬黎講，啲錢只係other people's money，最重要係management fee performance fee袋袋平安"},{"pid":"656d63eb932c17d5417f92da4e776b24b3d03972","tid":275313,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:20:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣防止被買呢啲垃圾債券</blockquote><br />\n睇實的強姦金"},{"pid":"326ae430e40ca50cc870f3d9c9ee098713a8a419","tid":275313,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T04:21:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣防止被買呢啲垃圾債券</blockquote><br />\n不入銀行"},{"pid":"56d285dc6093f131e31dae3667d42c25adb2a6f2","tid":275313,"uid":69088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:43:03.000Z","msg":"無講2年內不開<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=al3u4Y9mZyU%2BqV7qNFCnK54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=8089819e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】香港交易所(00388)行政總裁李小加稱，「債券通」的「南向通」仍未有開通時間表，要監管機構審批後，才有明確方向。"},{"pid":"a2a200a470928785bbc1ad6663ef4c7986645ebc","tid":275313,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T06:47:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點樣防止被買呢啲垃圾債券</blockquote><br />\n睇實的強姦金</blockquote><br />\n全部歐美<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eed57636be377d65e36f50c291ee6eb6566031a7","tid":275313,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:02:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無講2年內不開<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=al3u4Y9mZyU%2BqV7qNFCnK54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=8089819e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】香港交易所(00388)行政總裁李小加稱，「債券通」的「南向通」仍未有開通時間表，要監管機構審批後，才有明確方向。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n東方改左內文<br />\n<br />\n朝早篇新聞仲有講2年"}]}